                          <summary>A commentary of al-ʻaqāʼid al-nasafīyah</summary>
                                       <msItem xml:id="manuscript_13803-item1"> <author key="person_641145857886423020766" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/641145857886423020766" change="#ids-cleanup">
